            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-check"></i> Movie</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>We have more than 20,000 movies from IMDB, TMDB and Wiki. Type in the
                            name of one movie and you can get all the information of this movie: 
                            the directors, actors, filming locations, ratings, writers. If there
                            different movies with the same name, all the movies will be listed.</p>
                        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-default">Learn More</a> //xqiab-->
                        <form action="query/queryMovie" method="get">
                        	<p>Movie: <input type="text" name="moviename"></p>
                        	<input type="submit" value="Search Movie"/>
                        	<!-- <button type="button">Search Movie</button> -->
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-gift"></i> Actors</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>We have more than 20,000 actors from IMDB, TMDB and Wiki. Type in the
                            name of one actor and you can get all the information of this actor.
                            If there different actors with the same name, all the actors will be listed.</p>
                        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-default">Learn More</a> -->
                        <form action="query/queryActor" method="get">
                        	<p>Actor: <input type="text" name="actorname"></p>
                        	<input type="submit" value="Search Actor"/>
                        	<!-- <button type="button">Search Movie</button> -->
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-compass"></i> Build your own team</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Are you interested in building your own team for filming?
                            Type in the genre and you will get the best writer, director and actors
                            for this genre. Start to build your own team NOW!</p>
                        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-default">Learn More</a> -->
                        <form action="query/buildTeam" method="get">
                        	<p>Genre: <input type="text" name="genre"></p>
                        	<input type="submit" value="Build Team"/>
                        	<!-- <button type="button">Search Movie</button> -->
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-compass"></i> Find Movies in IMDB/TMDB/Wiki</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Find movies in the original data sources: IMDB, TMDB and Wiki,
                            we do data fusion, data resolution to merge data from different
                            sources to make sure you can get the most accuracy data.</p>
                        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-default">Learn More</a> -->
                        <form action="query/originalMovie" method="get">
                            <p>Movie: <input type="text" name="name"></p>
                            <p>Source: <input type="text" name="source"></p>
                            <input type="submit" value="Original Movie"/>
                            <!-- <button type="button">Search Movie</button> -->
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-compass"></i> Find Actors in IMDB/TMDB/Wiki</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Find actors in the original data sources: IMDB, TMDB and Wiki,
                            we do data fusion, data resolution to merge data from different
                            sources to make sure you can get the most accuracy data.</p>
                        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-default">Learn More</a> -->
                        <form action="query/originalActor" method="get">
                            <p>Actor: <input type="text" name="name"></p>
                            <p>Source: <input type="text" name="source"></p>
                            <input type="submit" value="Original Actor"/>
                            <!-- <button type="button">Search Movie</button> -->
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-compass"></i> Find Popular Movie</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Find the most popular movies in fused data base.
                            You can search by release year, genre.</p>
                        <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-default">Learn More</a> -->
                        <form action="query/popularfind" method="get">
                            <p>Genre: <input type="text" name="genre"></p>
                            <p>Year: <input type="text" name="year"></p>
                            <input type="submit" value="Popular Movie"/>
                            <!-- <button type="button">Search Movie</button> -->
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
